{\footnote # IDH_CSHARP_11}
{\footnote $ C# - LINQ (Language Integrated Query, C# 3+)}
{\footnote K C# LINQ;Language Integrated Query;Where Select OrderBy GroupBy Join;requete syntaxe methode;IEnumerable}
\b\fs24 LINQ (Language Integrated Query, C# 3+) \b0\fs20\par
\par
Syntaxe methode :\par
{\f1   var jeunes = personnes}\par
{\f1     .Where(p => p.Age < 30)}\par
{\f1     .OrderBy(p => p.Nom)}\par
{\f1     .Select(p => p.Nom)}\par
{\f1     .ToList();}\par
\par
Syntaxe requete :\par
{\f1   var jeunes = from p in personnes}\par
{\f1                where p.Age < 30}\par
{\f1                orderby p.Nom}\par
{\f1                select p.Nom;}\par
\par
Operateurs : Where, Select, SelectMany, OrderBy, ThenBy, GroupBy, Join,\par
GroupJoin, Distinct, Take, Skip, First, FirstOrDefault, Single, Any, All,\par
Count, Sum, Min, Max, Average, Aggregate, Zip, Chunk (.NET 6+).\par
\par
\par
