{\footnote # IDH_CSHARP_12}
{\footnote $ C# - async / await (C# 5+)}
{\footnote K C# async await;Task ValueTask;asynchrone;async streams;IAsyncEnumerable;HttpClient}
\b\fs24 async / await (C# 5+) \b0\fs20\par
\par
{\f1   public async Task<string> TelechargerAsync(string url) \{}\par
{\f1     using var client = new HttpClient();}\par
{\f1     var html = await client.GetStringAsync(url);}\par
{\f1     return html;}\par
{\f1   \}}\par
\par
{\f1   public async Task TraiterAsync() \{}\par
{\f1     var html = await TelechargerAsync("https://exemple.org");}\par
{\f1     Console.WriteLine(html.Length);}\par
{\f1   \}}\par
\par
Types de retour : Task, Task<T>, ValueTask, ValueTask<T>, void (event handlers\par
uniquement), IAsyncEnumerable<T> (C# 8+).\par
\par
Async streams (C# 8+) :\par
{\f1   public async IAsyncEnumerable<int> StreamAsync() \{}\par
{\f1     for (int i = 0; i < 10; i++) \{}\par
{\f1       await Task.Delay(100);}\par
{\f1       yield return i;}\par
{\f1     \}}\par
{\f1   \}}\par
{\f1   await foreach (var x in StreamAsync()) Console.WriteLine(x);}\par
\par
\par
